        "text": "Verdikta shiplog, Jul 13-20. Quiet week by the numbers — 0 merged PRs, 0 new stars across 5 public repos. But there's one real story."
      }
    },
    "tweet-2": {
      "type": "TweetCard",
      "props": {
        "text": "The docs stopped saying \"planned\" and started saying \"live.\" verdikta-docs and verdikta-dispatcher now document arbiter nodes, dispatcher contracts, and the bounties app as running on Base Mainnet — plus a new ReputationAggregator contract address on both mainnet and testnet."
      }
    },
    "tweet-3": {
      "type": "TweetCard",
      "props": {
        "text": "verdikta-applications bumped its user guide from Alpha-1 to Beta-1. An external contributor fixed a real UX papercut: the bounty work-product preview no longer forces a wallet connection first."
      }
    },
